metadata.name: HELTISHIA 01
metadata.description:
The first piece
She was born in a cold autumn evening. You will know her family in the next piece. Just know that when she was born, strange waves, forces and sounds were felt in the house and unusual creatures were seen in the house. Heltishia  grew up very soon and her friend was a teddy bear named Pepel .... She had no friends except Pepel..!
